#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.161:0.2"
msgid "13. Esanāvagga "
msgstr "13. Searches "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.161:0.3"
msgid "161. Esanāsutta "
msgstr "161. Searches "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.161:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.161:1.2"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, esanā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three searches. "

msgctxt "sn45.161:1.3"
msgid "Katamā tisso? "
msgstr "What three? "

msgctxt "sn45.161:1.4"
msgid "Kāmesanā, bhavesanā, brahmacariyesanā—"
msgstr "The search for sensual pleasures, the search for continued existence, and the search for a spiritual path. "

msgctxt "sn45.161:1.5"
msgid "imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso esanā. "
msgstr "These are the three searches. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.161:1.6"
msgid "Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ esanānaṃ abhiññāya ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabbo. "
msgstr "The noble eightfold path should be developed to directly know these three searches. "

msgctxt "sn45.161:1.7"
msgid "Katamo ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo? "
msgstr "What is the noble eightfold path? "

msgctxt "sn45.161:1.8"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe … sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant develops right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion, which rely on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and ripen as letting go. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.161:1.9"
msgid "Imāsaṃ kho, bhikkhave, tissannaṃ esanānaṃ abhiññāya ayaṃ ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo bhāvetabboti. "
msgstr "This is the noble eightfold path that should be developed to directly know these three searches.” "

